videos.description: Oregon uses good ball movement and gets it to Minyon Moore, who knocks down a 3-pointer from the corner.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One Play (Oregon's ball movement sets up Moore for the 3) 2020/02/14

videos.headline: Oregon's ball movement sets up Moore for the 3

videos.description: Sabrina Ionescu makes a nice pass between two defenders to Ruthy Hebard, who drives in for the layup.

videos.headline: Ionescu, Hebard link up for layup

videos.description: Chantel Horvat snags a loose ball, and UCLA takes it the other way where Charisma Osborne finishes with the bucket.

videos.description: Sabrina Ionescu tosses a pass to Ruthy Hebard from the top of the arc, and Hebard finishes with a layup.

videos.description: Sabrina Ionescu records her 1,000th career assist on a pass to Taylor Chavez for a 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Ionescu reaches 1,000 career assist
